lead_paragraph: New Zealand's 2-0 series defeat on home pitches by Australia was a disappointing end to the Brendon McCullum era and showed the Black Caps have work to do if they hope to consistently challenge the top test nations.

headline.print_headline: Analysis-Inconsistency Haunts New Zealand at End of McCullum Era
